r to try and stop the construction of a Wegmans Distribution Center.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 600;\">2020 Elections</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 400;\">During the 2020 municipal elections, Sunrise Richmond endorsed 6 candidates.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 1rem;\">While only 2 won, we are still extremely proud of their campaigns.</span></p><p dir=\"auto\" style=\"\"><font color=\"#050505\" face=\"Segoe UI Historic, Segoe UI, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.56px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Alexsis Rodgers - Mayor\r\nTavarris Spinks - 2nd District City Council\r\nAllan-Charles Chipman for 6th District City Council - 6th District City Council\r\nJoseph S. H. Rogers for 7th District City Council - 7th District City Council \r\nKenya Gibson - School Board 3rd District\r\nStephanie Rizzi for 5th District School Board - School Board 5th District</span></font></p>","email":"sunriserva@gmail.com","website":"https://join.slack.com/t/sunrisemovementrva/shared_invite/zt-kkr7e7qo-jrf0AmcjcRyjlXqo1V1xVQ","twitter":"https://twitter.com/SunriseMvmtRVA","facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/SunriseMvmtRVA/","instagram":"https://instagram.com/sunrisemvmtrva","signup":"https://bit.ly/SunriseRVAMail","donations":null,"websiteText":"Slack","logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/2e1e59d746e4b4f9a35c1ebaf690a82b/6d161/logo_1594769436.png.png","srcSet":"/static/2e1e59d746e4b4f9a35c1ebaf690a82b/94657/logo_1594769436.png.png 38w,\n/static/2e1e59d746e4b4f9a35c1ebaf690a82b/5db04/logo_1594769436.png.png 75w,\n/static/2e1e59d746e4b4f9a35c1ebaf690a82b/6d161/logo_1594769436.png.png 150w,\n/static/2e1e59d746e4b4f9a35c1ebaf690a82b/7e7e9/logo_1594769436.png.png 225w,\n/static/2e1e59d746e4b4f9a35c1ebaf690a82b/630fb/logo_1594769436.png.png 300w,\n/static/2e1e59d746e4b4f9a35c1ebaf690a82b/497c6/lo